                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </section>

              <!-- Section 10 -->
              <section id="changes" class="scroll-mt-8">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                  <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-mf-teal flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">10</div>
                  <h2 class="font-display text-h3 text-text-dark">Changes to Terms</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="pl-13 space-y-4 font-corp-body text-text-body">
                  <p>
                    We may update these Terms from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes by posting the new Terms on this page and updating the "Last updated" date. Your continued use of the Services after any changes constitutes acceptance of the new Terms.
